--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 Overview
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
This work is the result of an Amazon Kindle book named "Ray Tracing In One
Weekend." See the website:
https://in1weekend.blogspot.com/2016/01/ray-tracing-in-one-weekend.html

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 Usage
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
> cd /path/to/project
> source env/shell
> build
> ./raytrace --help